{"tid":526001,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"獅隧管道口多車串燒 入沙田大塞車","createTime":"2018-01-11T09:11:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-11T09:39:14.000Z","uid":1550,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fb3d7850c26c381b365f40f78364fff8b9744cdf","tid":526001,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T09:11:58.000Z","msg":"獅子山隧道公路發生交通意外，下午近4時，據報沙田方向近管道入口多部私家車連環相撞，援人員正趕往現場。<br />\n<br />\n運輸署表示，獅子山隧道公路往沙田方向近龍翔道的快線封閉，駕駛人士只可使用慢線行車。現時在獅子山隧道公路往沙田方向的車龍龍尾已到浸信會醫院。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180111/57694501\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180111%2F57694501&d=OqOhahmz45aXQeCbXoL6RwRJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=945ac9cc\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180111%2F57694501&h=9564a4aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180111/57694501</a>"},{"pid":"1e5499d8c3a22355a5ce6ac46f57ab4829810263","tid":526001,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T09:12:18.000Z","msg":"放工時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a539fc57b95c68af4baab22a76165a6414a2648","tid":526001,"uid":77196,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T09:13:59.000Z","msg":"點解炒極班司機都唔死 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07c741f95c2d0518f93d3ad847d47357fdf6bba8","tid":526001,"uid":101895,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T09:14:29.000Z","msg":"嘿嘿"},{"pid":"d8565ee3ddfe2190c2898eee627fc0fd6c27a0dc","tid":526001,"uid":42188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-11T09:15:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/11/171504_1a1c4e010a7924242daa56593d104cf3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?